{"word":"ὑφεῖσα","slug":"ὑφεῖσα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n109825\" key=\"u(fei=sa\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὑφεῖσα</orth>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ion.\">Ion.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὕπεισα</orth>, <sense id=\"n109825.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">I placed under</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">secretly,</tr_> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὑπείσας ἄνδρας</foreign> (<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ion.\">Ion.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ part.\">part.</a></mood>) <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">having set</tr_> them <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">in ambush,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:126\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.126</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:103\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.103</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">λόχον ὑφείσας</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0577.tlg001:55J\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Nic.Dam.\">Nic.Dam.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">55J.</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: but as (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ὑφ-</etym>)<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εἷσα</foreign> is the augmented <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ aor.\">aor.</a></tns> of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἑδ-</foreign> (cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">καθίζω,</foreign> <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Att.\">Att.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ fut.\">fut.</a></tns> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">καθέσω</foreign>), the <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ part.\">part.</a></mood> must be unaugmented, and <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὑπέσας, ὑπέσαντες</foreign> shd. be restored in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> </bibl> ll. cc., and either <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὑφέσας</foreign> or the later form <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὑφίσας [ῐ]</foreign> (cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὑφίζω</foreign>) in Nic.Dam.l.c.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}